In the [[British Police]], '''"Woodentop"''' is a [[slang]] term used by [[Criminal Investigation Department]] detectives to refer to uniformed police officers. It may be a reference to the wooden construction of a bobby's [[custodian helmet]].

It was also the name of the pilot episode of the long-running [[television]] programme ''[[The Bill]]''.
